{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was coal burning where they were heating up these bits, and they were sharpening it and putting them together, so I was able to catch a-- a bit of a sleep there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was there for about approximately no more than four weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember one incident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were always-- you know, there were many conveyor belts, from side shafts coming into a main shaft.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a big conveyor that was taking the stuff out to a main silo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, one of these people from the Todt organization said that the conveyor belt was sabotaged, and somebody cut out a piece from the conveyor belt for a sole of a shoe, you know?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a very serious problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as our detail, on the way-- when we were-- when our shift was finished-- I was working on the night shift-- we were all lined up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the SS officer came, and he said, who cut, who sabotaged the conveyor belt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, there were hundreds of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, you have two minutes, whoever did this, to come forward.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after two minutes, nobody came forward.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he just went and he counted-- he told his orderly to count every 10th man in the line and take out-- bring out the 10th man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they collected several people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think there were about 12 or so all together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were lined up against the wall and shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was lucky to be right in the middle, in between the 10, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so these are the kind of things that happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
